
<h1 class="app-text">Sobre mi</h1>
<br>
<div class="row">

  <div class="col-md-4">
    <%= image_tag "https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/devcamp-portfolio-jcc/uploads/portfolio/main_image/astronaut.jpg", width:300, alt: "Imagen de perfil" %>
    
    <div class="skills">
      <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
        <div class="skill">
          <h5 class= "app-text text-left"><%= skill.title %>:</h5>
          <div class="progress">
            <div 
            class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-success"
            role="progressbar"
            aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
            aria-valuemax="100"
            style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

  </div>  
  
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <p class="app-text text-left">En esta página aparecerá la parte relativa tanto a la experiencia laboral como a los diversos cursos que se hayan realizado. Con respecto a los trabajos realizados está la parte de 'portfolio' y aquí no aparecerían aunque también se podrían enlazar desde aquí.</p>

    <p class="app-text text-left">El perfil que aparece no es real y solo está puesto con fines educativos.</p>

    <br>
    
    <p class="text-left">
      <button
        class = "btn btn-success"
        type = "button"
        color = black;
        data-toggle = "collapse"
        data-target = "#jobHistory"
        aria-expanded = "false"
        aria-controler ="jobHistory"
      >
        Experiencia Profesional
      </button>

       <button
        class = "btn btn-success"
        type = "button"
        color = black;
        data-toggle = "collapse"
        data-target = "#education"
        aria-expanded = "false"
        aria-controler ="education"
      >
        Educación Recibida
      </button>
      
       <button
        class = "btn btn-success"
        type = "button"
        color = black;
        data-toggle = "collapse"
        data-target = "#works"
        aria-expanded = "false"
        aria-controler ="education"
      >
        Trabajos Publicados
      </button>

    </p>
    
    <p>
      <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory" >
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          MIT - Massachusetts Institute of Technology, 1998 - 2002
        </div>
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          ESA - European Space Agency, 2002 - 2009
        </div>
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          CERN - Conseil Européen pour la Recherche Nucléaire, 2009 - 2015
        </div>
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          SpaceX - Space Exploration Technologies Corporation, 2015 - <%= Date.today.year %>
        </div>
        <br>
      </div>

      <div class="collapse" id="education" >
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          Stanford University - Aerospace engineering, 1985 - 1989
        </div>
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          MIT - Computer Science, 1989 - 1992
        </div>
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          New York University - Brain and Cognitive Sciences, 1992 - 1994
        </div>
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          ETH Zurich (Swiss Federal Institute of Technology)- Nuclear Engineering , 1994 - 1996
        </div>
        <br>
      </div>

      <div class="collapse" id="works" >
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          'Study of neural network implementation in complex computer systems', 1995
        </div>
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          'Practical use of gravitational fields in quantum physics', 1997
        </div>
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          'Use of <i>amanita muscaria</i> in shamanic rituals in the Tuvan region', 1997
        </div>
        <div class="app-text text-left">
          'Practical study of interlacing subatomic particles of information teleportation' , 2002
        </div>
        <br>
      </div>

    </p>

  </div>

</div>
